Q.4) CHANGE THE ADDRESS,CITY,PHONE NUMBER OF A PARTICULAR CUSTOMER


mysql> select * from customers;
+-----+----------+------------+-----------+------------+
| cid | name     | address    | city      | phn_no     |
+-----+----------+------------+-----------+------------+
|   1 | prasanth | koduvally  | kozhikode | 1234567890 |
